snippet.title: Furquest LAUNCH TRAILER! (Talkshow Boy - I Cut Myself)
snippet.description:
🍓▸Play on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1740230/Furquest/
🍇▸Join the Discord! http://discord.gg/Be2KtRmhBK
🍐▸All my social media! https://linktr.ee/thebittersoul
Promotional artwork by @tsanapi !!

--

The Best Character Ever is Valentine in my game Furquest! UNDERTALE 2?! Maybe! It's a Deltarune style game, Deltarune Chapter 2 is pretty Mind Blowing, Deltarune Chapters 1+2 are great, Undertale - Megalovania is also a great song! Deltarune Is An Experience, I swear!!  Deltarune Analysis is also pretty fun!

Omori & WarioWare are also big inspirations! Face Your Fears, be brave, plays Omori, and have fun! This was a very funny video with lots of laughs!! Undertale - The Ultimate Undertale & Deltarune Iceberg is a fantastic video you should also check out! :)
